cs.CR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.DS 

The paper discusses security and privacy implications of machine learning as a service (MLaaS) and proposes attacks and defenses against membership inference attacks. This topic falls under the sub-category of computer security (cs.CR) as well as machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), and data structures (cs.DS) as these fields are all relevant to the study of MLaaS and membership inference attacks.
